✅ 使用方法
假设你的目录是：
./assets/dual_arm_and_single_arm/objects/object_sim/
  alarmclock/object.xml
  mug/object.xml
  ...

1）先 dry-run（只看哪些会改）
"python patch_object_sim_objectxml.py \
  ./assets/dual_arm_and_single_arm/objects/object_sim \
  --dry-run"
你会看到类似：
[PATCH] .../alarmclock/object.xml | pos_changed=True freejoint_inserted=True

2）确认无误后，真正写回（会自动生成 .bak 备份）
"python patch_object_sim_objectxml.py \
  ./assets/dual_arm_and_single_arm/objects/object_sim"

3）如果某些 object.xml 里 <body name="object"> 没有 pos，你想补 pos
"python patch_object_sim_objectxml.py \
  ./assets/dual_arm_and_single_arm/objects/object_sim \
  --add-pos-if-missing"
✅ 快速验证是否改成功（命令行）
"grep -R --line-number 'pos="[^"]* 0.6 [^"]*"' ./assets/dual_arm_and_single_arm/objects/object_sim/*/object.xml
    grep -R --line-number '<freejoint name="object_free"' ./assets/dual_arm_and_single_arm/objects/object_sim/*/object.xml"